snippet: A man charged Tuesday with fatally stabbing a 75-year-old woman he didn't know in a Duluth grocery store told investigators he went to the store to "either shop or kill somebody," a criminal complaint alleges....

headline.print_headline: Man Charged in Fatal Attack on Shopper
headline.main: Man Charged in Fatal Attack on Shopper

lead_paragraph: A man charged Tuesday with fatally stabbing a 75-year-old woman he didn't know in a Duluth grocery store told investigators he went to the store to "either shop or kill somebody," a criminal complaint alleges.
